    'hype.howItWorksContent2': 'Step 1 — Pace. Nightlife sales are back-loaded (most tickets sell in the final days). We learn the typical sales curve from your past events and compare your current sales to where they "should" be at this point in the countdown.',
    'hype.howItWorksContent3': 'Step 2 — Demand. We read the leading signals that come before a purchase: traffic vs your normal day, the view → cart → checkout → buy funnel, time on page, returning visitors, favorites and traffic sources. This adjusts the pace projection up or down.',
